extends layout

block content
  h1.text-2xl.font-semibold.mb-8 Privacy Policy

  article.bg-surface.rounded-xl.border.border-border-default(style="padding: 2rem;")
    .prose.prose-invert.text-text-secondary(style="line-height: 1.7;")
      p.text-text-muted.text-sm(style="margin-bottom: 2rem;") Last updated: February 2026

      h2.text-lg.font-semibold.text-text-primary(style="margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;") What data we collect

      p StraightToYourAI collects the following data when you use the extension:

      ul(style="margin: 1rem 0; padding-left: 1.5rem;")
        li
          strong URLs and titles
          |  of pages you choose to save
        li
          strong Content extracts
          |  (YouTube transcripts, web page text) from pages you save
        li
          strong Anonymous identifier
          |  stored in a cookie to link your collections across sessions

      h2.text-lg.font-semibold.text-text-primary(style="margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;") What we don't collect

      ul(style="margin: 1rem 0; padding-left: 1.5rem;")
        li No personal information (name, email, etc.)
        li No browsing history (we only see pages you explicitly save)
        li No invasive analytics (see Anonymous usage analytics below)
        li No data shared with third parties

      h2.text-lg.font-semibold.text-text-primary(style="margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;") How data is stored

      p Your data is stored on servers hosted by #[a.text-red-500(href="https://supabase.com" target="_blank") Supabase] (PostgreSQL database). Your anonymous identifier is stored in an HTTP-only cookie that cannot be accessed by JavaScript.

      h2.text-lg.font-semibold.text-text-primary(style="margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;") Third-party services

      p We use the following third-party services:

      ul(style="margin: 1rem 0; padding-left: 1.5rem;")
        li
          strong Jina Reader
          |  (r.jina.ai) - to extract content from web pages you save
        li
          strong YouTube
          |  - to extract video transcripts from videos you save

      p These services receive the URL of pages you choose to save. No other data is shared.

      h2.text-lg.font-semibold.text-text-primary(style="margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;") Anonymous usage analytics

      p We collect anonymous usage events to understand how the extension is used (e.g. which AI provider is selected, which export method is used). This data is sent to #[a.text-red-500(href="https://posthog.com" target="_blank") PostHog].

      ul(style="margin: 1rem 0; padding-left: 1.5rem;")
        li Only action types are tracked (e.g. "opened in Claude", "copied markdown")
        li No URLs, page titles, video titles, or content is ever sent
        li Your anonymous identifier is used solely to count unique users
        li No personal information is collected or shared

      h2.text-lg.font-semibold.text-text-primary(style="margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;") Data deletion

      p You can delete your collections at any time from the #[a.text-red-500(href="/collections") My Collections] page. To completely reset your account, use the #[a.text-red-500(href="/disconnect") Disconnect] feature.

      h2.text-lg.font-semibold.text-text-primary(style="margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;") Contact

      p For any questions about this privacy policy, contact us at #[a.text-red-500(href="mailto:tomyai@plstry.me" target="_blank") tomyai@plstry.me].
